    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers broadly to articles associated with or used in the context of a ceremony, which includes formal acts conducted elaborately, solemnly, and as prescribed by the ritual or protocol of religious, state, court, social, or tribal procedure.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
